Recorded live at California State University in Northridge, California on October 23, 1991.


Sourced from the commercial bootleg Live At The Quad, this is a document of Rage Against The Machine's first official show, at

California State University during lunch break. The quality's not great - in addition, there's a little static in places during

the first track and a slight skip at the start of Township Rebellion. Despite that, this is an essential boot for historical

reasons. Many of the songs are unreleased, and even those that did appear on the first album often sport alternate lyrics here.


1. Killing in the Name (Instrumental)
2. Take the Power Back
3. Autologic
4. Bullet in the Head
5. Hit the Deck
6. Township Rebellion
7. Darkness of Greed
8. Clear the Lane
9. Clampdown (The Clash Cover)
10. Know Your Enemy
11. Freedom
